      <section eId="sec_44_13_87">
        <num>44-13-87</num>
        <content>
          <p>The applicant for exemption from levy and sale of property under this article shall be permitted to select the property to be exempted but not to exceed the amount allowed by law.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1872, p. 43, § 7; Code 1873, § 2039; Code 1882, § 2039; Civil Code 1895, § 2862; Civil Code 1910, § 3412; Code 1933, § 51-1008; Ga. L. 1983, p. 1170, § 2.)</p>
